These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, april
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, billiard
1. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
3. the person playing billiard is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday         | october | february   | april |
| Game   | poker | billiard | scrabble        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, family, horror
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, r&b, soul
1. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the fan of reggae##7
2. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
3. the fan of r&b is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | thriller   | family   |
| Music-Genre        | r&b | soul | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, reading
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, juice
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
2. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person drinking iced-tea##7
3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby        | magic-tricks | reading | traveling |
| Beverage   | iced-tea       | juice     | hot-chocolate         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
House: craftsman, tower, gothic-revival
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, traveling
1. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the tower house##8
2. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the craftsman house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| House           | craftsman | gothic-revival | tower |
| Hobby   | traveling  | skydiving | rock-climbing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, old-henry, bongani
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
4. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
6. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Game   | backgammon | poker | whist |
| Cigar           | old-henry    | bongani      | ritmeester  |

