.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, chess
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, punk, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
2. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
3. the person playing chess is not to the right of the fan of house##8
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Game   | billiard | canasta | chess |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | punk   | house     |

