.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, december, june
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Hobby   | chess | cooking | skydiving |
| Birthday        | june      | december    | september |

