.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, apricot, coral
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, june
1. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
2. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Color          | coral | fuchsia  | apricot |
| Birthday   | october     | september | june   |

