.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-10::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski
3 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, dog
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski        | boat    |
| Pet      | chinchilla  | dog | mouse |

