.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-11::.
City: venice, paris, hannover
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea, zinnia
1. the person traveling to hannover is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |     3     |
| City   | paris    | hannover | venice |
| Flower    | azalea | dahlia   | zinnia     |

