2. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the aristoff-smoker##8
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | aristoff | vegafina |
| Beverage   | sprite  | 7up    | fanta    |

 